body:
@AudriusButkevicius Oh I don't mind the Options fields as such, certainly not from a bloat perspective at least. And given that fields can be added at the end of the message without impacting compatibility, we should be fine with the changes proposed.

I just don't want us to end up wanting a _flags_ field somewhere and going "Hey, we have []Options, lets just add an option called "flags" with the flags as a string formatted integer" because that would be :hankey:

There'll be at least one v0.11 with space for breaking changes before v1.0, and we for sure won't be releasing v1.0 in two weeks, so don't worry, we'll get all the breaks in there. :)
